Entry boasts wood flooring extending into Formal Dining & Den. Den has 18' ceiling, fireplace w/granite surround, built-ins. Kitchen w/granite countertops, 42'' maple cabinets, travertine backsplash, stainless steel appliances. Swanky WINE ROOM w/etched concrete flooring & stone accent wall. Covered patio & gazebo for entertaining. Double hung windows throughout! WOW!


Please visit my MLS Site http://SearchMLSByMonica.net for more current listings or my buyer's website http://BuyRealEstateMonica.com for Buyer info and testimonials. Check out my fan page http://RealtyByMonicaFanPage.com for the latest news.  Ask about my Buyer's REBATE!
